 Dear Naukri Mili Job Placement India,


 Today’s COO has to think beyond just optimising resources and increasing efficiencies. They have to keep an eye on current and future challenges. To do this, they must develop multi-pronged strategies that span operating model, cost structure, market footprint, and tech-driven innovation. This creates a strong CEO-COO partnership: crucial for businesses to unlock their transformative potential.
 
 
 STARTS
 ON
 
29 December, 2024


 DURATION & FORMAT
 

 12 Months
 

 Live online sessions + campus immersion (by IIMK), 2 online certificate courses by Kellogg Executive Education
 


 PROGRAMME
 FEE
 
INR 6,50,000 + GST


 To complement this exciting, evolving role, IIM Kozhikode has launched the second batch of its Chief Operations Officer (COO) Programme. Designed for seasoned operations and supply chain leaders, the programme will equip you with technology and data driven strategic mindset to enable customer-centric value creation and achieve strategic operational excellence. You will hone your financial acumen, C-suite leadership quotient, executive presence, capabilities to spearhead transformation and change management. Participants will gain the global edge through two online certificate courses from Kellogg Executive Education.
 

