 IIM Kozhikode Executive Alumni Status
 

Live Online Lectures by IIMK Faculty

2 online modules by Kellogg Executive Education

3-Day Immersion IIM Kozhikode’s Campus with a leadership building workshop

Capstone Project guided by IIMK Faculty

Hands-On Business Simulations in Supply Chain and Leadership

Insights from industry practitioners for a real-world perspective

Networking Opportunities with CXO Peers

Annual Subscription to the Wall Street Journal

