APPLY NOW 

Who Should Participate in This Programme?


 This programme is carefully curated for:
 
	- Operations leaders and aspiring COOs looking to strengthen knowledge with cutting-edge topics in technology, design thinking, AI, digital supply chain, agile, and risk resilience; and keen to build valuable networks, deepen insights, and develop C-Suite leadership skills with a focus on efficiency and resilience.
	- New and evolving COOs who want to focus on cutting-edge practices for driving efficiency, innovation, and growth; and keen to enhance strategic skills for optimal operations, strengthen relationships with influential leaders, and foster collaboration.

Key Learning Outcomes

	- Master everyday efficiencies including in digital and engineering operations
	- Create ‘big picture’ alignment by working in line with C-Suite goals
	- Drive smarter decisions and value-chain innovation with new technology
	- Create shock-proof operations with risk and regulatory management
	- Orchestrate all functions to achieve breakthrough success

